title: The Ultimate Art Bell Collection (Part 2 of 2)
description:
The Ultimate Art Bell Collection (Part 2 of 2)



Thanks for taking the time to download this torrent. 

This project was a labor of love, and I couldn't have done it without the help of many people. I would like to thank bellgab.com for creating a community
for people to connect and share these Art Bell shows. 

Included in the "Shows" folder are 1200+ Art Bell shows spanning from 1993-2013. It is the most complete and accurate collection available online. Every show is tagged with i3dv2.3 tags,
which will allow the files to be easily incorporated into your favorite music management software. The filenames/titles are also optimized for online streaming through shoutcast
or icecast.

Included in the "Extras" folder are all sorts of extra goodies related to Art Bell and his show Coast to Coast AM. There are PDFs of the AfterDark magazine, lists of shows, website snapshots 
of the old Coast to Coast and Dreamland websites, and a large collection of Phil Hendrie paradies. There are even two audiobooks for you to enjoy. 

So, go on and enjoy. It has been my pleasure to provide these classic shows
